---
---

<section class="bg-black overflow-hidden">
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-16">
    <!-- Left: heading with gold blob -->
    <div
      data-reveal="left"
      class="px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-8 lg:py-14 bg-gold lg:rounded-r-full lg:flex lg:items-center lg:self-stretch"
    >
      <h2 class="text-black font-bold leading-tight text-h1 text-center lg:text-left">
        Why Choose Duartes<br />
        <span class="text-black">Auto Detailing?</span>
      </h2>
    </div>

    <!-- Right: text + stats -->
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-6 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-8 lg:py-14 lg:self-stretch">
      <p
        data-reveal="up"
        style="--reveal-delay: 100ms"
        class="text-gold font-semibold text-lg italic"
      >
        "It's not just a cleaning—it's a transformation."
      </p>
      <p
        data-reveal="up"
        style="--reveal-delay: 200ms"
        class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed"
      >
        At Duartes Auto Detailing, we believe true detailing is about more than just washing a car. It is about carefully restoring the condition, presentation, and protection of every vehicle we work on. We bring professional mobile service, quality products, and attention to detail directly to our clients, delivering results with the convenience of service at your home or office.
      </p>

      <!-- Stats -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 mt-4">
        <div
          data-reveal="up"
          style="--reveal-delay: 200ms"
          class="flex flex-col gap-1 text-center"
        >
          <span class="text-gold font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl">5,000+</span>
          <span class="text-text-muted text-sm">Vehicles Detailed</span>
        </div>
        <div
          data-reveal="up"
          style="--reveal-delay: 300ms"
          class="flex flex-col gap-1 text-center"
        >
          <span class="text-gold font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl">3</span>
          <span class="text-text-muted text-sm">Years of Experience</span>
        </div>
        <div
          data-reveal="up"
          style="--reveal-delay: 400ms"
          class="flex flex-col gap-1 text-center"
        >
          <span class="text-gold font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl">1,000+</span>
          <span class="text-text-muted text-sm">Locations Served</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
